dct_title_s: A correct map of Antient Greece
dct_description_sm: Conder sculp. ; Engraved for Millar's New Complete & Universal System of Geography.
Shows various cities and towns, waterways, islands, regional names.
Inset map shows area south of the Strait of Messina.
Likely taken from George Henry Millar's "The new and universal system of geography : being a complete history and description of the whole world..." (circa 1782).
